name: Roget’s International Thesaurus of English Words and Phrases
description: Mawson, C. O. Sylvester (Christopher Orlando Sylvester), 1870–1938, ed. Roget’s international thesaurus of English words and phrases; a complete book of synonyms and antonyms founded upon and embodying Roget’s original work, with numerous additions and modernizations, by C. O. Sylvester Mawson.
